<sect1 id="dir_e1a38fd6dc0543c7f97fb1ccf1615de7_1autotoc_md280">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics</title><para>High-level gameplay mechanics and systems for game logic.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_e1a38fd6dc0543c7f97fb1ccf1615de7_1autotoc_md281">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the core building blocks for implementing game mechanics. It contains components that store game state and systems that implement game rules according to the composition-over-inheritance principle.</para>
</sect1>
